

**Matsh g Jesus doaj g pi neadam **

1 Kuchd am hihim. D ab haha wabsh hema daha g oꞌodham ch e‑mahsidag amjed pi nea. 2 Kuchd ab kakke g Jesus, “Neh, t‑mashchamdam, dohꞌo d chuꞌijig mo d pi neadam ihda oꞌodham? No d hejel chuꞌijigaj aha no d geꞌegedgaj ha‑chuꞌijig?” 

3 D hab kaij g Jesus, “Id o pi hab d shaꞌi ahga mas d ha‑chuꞌijig. Heg o hekaj pi nea mat g Jiosh am wo chehgi g e‑gewkdag ab amjed. 4 Am att hab wo junihid g chikpanaj hegai mat ia i ni‑ahꞌad mo idani am kia wiꞌis g tash no pi ab him mamt hahawa pi wo e nako. 5 Dani tonlig am em‑wehhejed mani ia em‑wehmaj.” 

6 D hab cheꞌiok g Jesus k am siswua jewed dahm k am hab juh g bid k hekaj ab bidsh g wuhpuij hegai pi neadam 7 k hab ahg, “Am g him k ab i wakon g e‑wuhiosha heg eda woꞌo mo hab e aꞌaga Siloam.” \(K hab d ahga ihda “I Ahꞌad.”\) T wa woho am hih ihda pi neadam k am wako g e‑wuhiosha k am i uhpam jiwia s‑ap haꞌichu neidch. 

8 Hegam mo s‑mahch ch hegam mo si neid mo wabsh haꞌichu ha tahni ad am i neidok hab kaij, “Aha no pi woho d hegai mo am dahiwup ch haꞌichu ha tahni?” 

9 D haꞌi hab kaij mo d hegai. D haꞌi hab ep kaij, “Pi o d hegai. Ho o wabsh si wepo mahs.” 

D hekaj hab kaij ihda mo wa pi neakahim, “Dani ahni.” 

10 Kumd ab ep kakke, “Shahpt masma nent?” 

11 D hab kaij, “Hegai mash d Jesus at ab bidsh g ni‑wuhpui am jewedo siswuak k hab ni‑ahg mant wo him k wo wako g ni‑wuhiosha am Siloam woꞌo ch ed. Kunt am him k hab wabsh chum ni‑wakon k ha hekaj s‑ap haꞌichu neid.” 

12 D hab kaij idam, “T hebai hih?” 

Kud hab hahawa kaij mo pi mahch mas hebai hih. 

**Mash g Palasi am mamche g doajida **

13 D am wa haꞌi bei ihda oꞌodham mo wa pi nea am Palasi ha wui. 14 K d t‑mihshmda tash mad eda g Jesus hab juh ihda. 15 D g Palasi ab hahawa kakke mas has masma nent. 

D hab kaij, “Hegai Jesus at ab bidsh g ni‑wuhpui am siswuak jewedo. Nt ab i wako g ni‑wuhiosha k hahawa s‑ap haꞌichu neid.” 

16 D haꞌi hab kaij hegam Palasi, “Neh, pi o ab hu shaꞌi Jiosh amjed nat pi melchkwua g t‑chehanig hab juhk ihda t‑mihshmda tash ed.” 

D am aꞌai e wui gegokiwua g hemajkam nad pi haꞌijj hab epai kaij, “Pi at wo e nako g pi ap chuꞌijkam mas hab mahs s‑hasig haꞌichu hab wo juh.” 

17 D heg hekaj ab ep si kakke hegam Palasi, “Shahp i elid hegai oꞌodham map hab kaij mat m‑nench.” 

D hab kaij, “Bani elid mo d ge Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam.” 

18 D wabshaba pi wohochud idam hahaꞌichu mas wa woho d pi neadam ch am ha waid g geꞌegedgaj 19 ch muꞌi haꞌichu ha kakke mas d ha‑aliga ihda ch ga hu i e‑mahsidag amjed pi nea, kch ehp mas has masma hahawa haꞌichu neid. 

20 D hab hahawa kaij g geꞌegedgaj mo d ha‑aliga ch ga hu e‑mahsidag amjed pi nea 21 ch wabshaba pi mahch mas has masma s‑ap haꞌichu neid ch ep pi mahch mas hedai doaj ch ab ha ahgid mat wo kakke no pi d geꞌe k ch hejel am wo e ah. 

22-23 Hegam hahaꞌichu ad wa am heki hu apꞌech mat pi wo ha hiwigi mat am hu ep wo i wahp cheopi ch ed hegam mat hedam hab wo chei mo g Jesus d Jiosh si Kehsha. D heg hekaj s‑ha ehbid g geꞌegedgaj ch hab kaij mat ab wo kakke, t hejel am wo e ah. 

24 D ab ep i wai g Palasi ihda mat bei g e‑nendag k hab ahg, “Am g t‑ahgid g wohokam mapt ab wo hehgchul g Jiosh. S‑mahch ach mo ihda has chehgi d pi ap chuꞌijkam.” 

25 D hab kaij ihda mat bei g e‑nendag: “Pi ani shaꞌi mahch mas d pi ap chuꞌijkam ch wabshaba id s‑ap s‑mahch mani pi neakahim ch hemuch haha wabsh si s‑nea.” 

26 D idam ab hahawa ep kakke, “T has m‑juh k m‑nench?” 

27 D hab kaij, “M ani wa heki hu em‑ahgid. Mt pi ab hu ni‑kaiha. A m haschu ahgch ab ep ni‑kakke? Aha namt ahpim hab waꞌap ab wo i s‑wohoch mo d Jiosh si Kehsha?” 

28 D idam ab si s‑kehꞌid ch hab kaij, “Ahpi apt ab i s‑wohoch hegai hemajkam. Ahchim ach hi g Mosesbad ab s‑wohochud. 29 S‑mahch ach mo g Jiosh g Mosesbad ab haꞌichu ahgid. Kuch pi shaꞌi mahch mas hebai amjed him hegai.” 

30 D hab kaij ihda, “M haschu ahgch pi mahch mas hebai amjed him. T eda ab i ni‑nench. 31 S‑mahch ach mo g Jiosh pi ab hu kaiham g pi ap chuꞌijkam ch wabshaba ab ha kaiham hegam mo ab si has elid ch am hab junihim g tatchuij. 32 Pi ach hekid shaꞌi kah mas hedai i nench hegai mo e‑mahsidag amjed pi nea. 33 T hi wo wa e nako hema mat hab wo juh ihda hab mahs haꞌichu matp ab Jiosh amjed wo himad.” 

34 D ab si s‑koꞌokam has ahg ch hab kaij, “Dap wabsh si hekia pi apꞌekam ga huꞌi e‑mahsidag amjed ch eda chum haꞌichu t‑mashcham.” D amjed gam hu si i wuhshad cheopi t amjed k pi hiwigi mas am ep wo i wah. 

**Mash hedai pi nea Jiosh apꞌedag ed **

35 D kah g Jesus mamt i wuhshad k am i gahghim k hab kaij am i chehgiok, “Nap ab si hiwig g Jiosh si Kehsha?” 

36 D hab kaij ihda oꞌodham, “A k hedai wud. Am g ni‑ahgid. Nt ab wo si i hiw.” 

37 D hab kaij g Jesus, “Dani ahni map hahawa s‑ap ni‑neid mant wa m‑nench.” 

38 D ab si i gei wui k hab kaij, “Ab ani si m‑hiwig, s‑apꞌekam ni‑kownalig.” 

39 D hab hahawa kaij g Jesus, “Ia ant jiwia jewed dahm mant wo mahsko wua mo hedai pi nea ch hedai s‑nea id eda Jiosh apꞌedag.” 

40 D haꞌi am gegok g Palasi ch si has i elid k hab kaij, “Nap ahchim hab ep chum t‑ahg mach hab waꞌap pi nenea.” 

41 D hab kaij g Jesus, “Pi amt ab hu wo em‑abch mamtp wo wohokamch mam pi nenea am Jiosh apꞌedag ed. M wabshaba hab chum kaij mam s‑nenea.” 

